column5: May it go quickly for those on the 24 hr diet-even you too Roy !  6 30 pm tomorrow can't come quicker. I usually cave around the 20 hr mark-ssshhhhh
My buddy had to fast for 12 hours... He didn't pay attention... He thought it was 24 hours....  Worst part... We figured this out 11 hours before his appointment... Lol....
Oh,that thang..  Did it two years ago. Woke up half way through. Was not good. After my first time ever,I was very sick for 2 months.
I'm with you Darren.  It's all just a conspiracy to keep us away from the smoked meat for a day.
I'm glad you guys cleared that up----I thought it was a description of some woman you knew!!
I almost made it until lunch, made an appearance at synagogue though....
